# Deployment checklist for package.json

Ensure these scripts exist:
- "start": "node server.js"  — for production
- "server": "nodemon server.js" — for local development

When deploying:
- Set Node version to 18+ (check .nvmrc or specify in hosting platform)
- Do NOT commit node_modules
- Make sure all dependencies in package.json are production deps
- Development deps (nodemon) are fine and will be skipped in production
